Name: epidemic typhus
Definition: A typhus that has_material_basis _in Rickettsia prowazekii

Name: endemic typhus
Definition: A typhus that has_material_basis_in Rickettsia typhi or has_material_basis_in Rickettsia felis

Name: obsolete lymphangitis-associated rickettsiosis
Definition: A typhus that has_material_basis_in Rickettsia typhi or has_material_basis_in Rickettsia felis

Name: obsolete Rickettsia aeschlimannii spotted fever
Definition: A typhus that has_material_basis_in Rickettsia typhi or has_material_basis_in Rickettsia felis

Name: scrub typhus
Definition: A typhus that has_material_basis_in Orientia tsutsugamushi
Synonym: Typhus fever due to Rickettsia tsutsugamushi
